Affected areas inclue Glenvista, Mulbarton, Bassonia, Liefde and Vrede. JOHANNESBURG - Several areas in the south of Johannesburg are without electricity on Tuesday morning. City Power says that technicians are trying to restore electricity to the Prospect sub-station. Affected areas inclue Glenvista, Mulbarton, Bassonia, Liefde and Vrede. It is understood that the Mulbarton substation is also experiencing interruptions.  